body:
# hola
I love data. Here are some mini-projects I've done in my spare time.

# visualizations
Most of these are done in D3.



# data analysis notebooks
These are notebooks for mini-projects on web-scraping, data analysis and visualization. The impetus for each is a simple question such as "What place in the U.S. is most removed from any National Landmark?"
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
